No, not that one.
The other one, there!

01:21:56.370 --> 01:21:57.997
Yeah, there.
The one in the tights.

01:21:58.080 --> 01:21:59.707
Look, grandma,
it's her.

01:22:01.292 --> 01:22:03.294
Get away from me.
Get away from me.

01:22:03.377 --> 01:22:05.713
Don't let her
get away.

01:22:05.796 --> 01:22:07.256
Get away from me!

01:22:10.551 --> 01:22:13.679
Hey! Get me
out of here! Help!

01:22:15.932 --> 01:22:19.185
