by ship?

01:26:34.940 --> 01:26:36.734
First class.

01:26:36.817 --> 01:26:38.569
The best cabin.

01:26:38.652 --> 01:26:40.988
The best of everything.

01:26:44.116 --> 01:26:46.493
Good night, grandma.

01:26:47.036 --> 01:26:49.413
Good night, Luke.

